This is the installation file for the gpi_send package.

MANDATORY PREREQUISITES
-----------------------

Qt5 Toolkit, v5.9 or better (http://www.qt.io/).

libgpiod, v2.2.1 or later (https://libgpiod.readthedocs.io/en/master/).
 Low-level library for interacting with General Purpose Input/Output (GPIO)
 devices on Linux.
